'''Threaten''' is a 1-cost Basic '''Hostility''' card for [[Sal]]. It deals 1-4 base damage. As a base card '''Threaten''' is always part of the available card pool for [[Sal]].

==Upgrades==
After accruing 6 experience '''Threaten''' is able to be upgraded. Like every basic card, '''Threaten''' has more than two upgrades, from which it randomly picks 2 you can decide from.
